---
title: Summer Mango & Pear Crumble with Mint Cream | Serves 4+
description: Beat the Christmas summer heat with a refreshing slice of this fruitilicious crumble, perfect for eating outside surrounded by
friends and family. We’re baking the most tropical of fruit, mango and pear into a golden crumble so you can finish the festivities
off with a flourish of decadence.
